data.title: Pororo Gonglyong-woldeu
data.synopsis:
Oh my gosh! A scary giant dinosaur ordered the pink dino Kong to bring one of Pororo's friends back to his planet. Their invasion to the Earth has begun! Meanwhile, the great inventor Eddy finishes his work on new outfits for the Pororo heroes. The outfits have some special power that will help the heroes to fight against dino Kong. Would the Pororo heroes be able to defeat the dinosaurs?

(Source: Amazon Prime)

titles.title: Hana wa Saku, Shura no Gotoku

data.title: Hana wa Saku, Shura no Gotoku
data.synopsis:
Hana lives on the small island of Tonakijima, with a population of 600, and loves reading to the island's children. Mizuki, the president of the school's broadcasting club, notices Hana's talent for engaging others through her storytelling and invites her to join the club. As Hana embarks on this new journey, she experiences many "firsts" with the broadcasting club members, deepening her love for reading even more.

(Source: MAL News)

data.title: Gachiakuta
data.synopsis:
Living in the slums of a wealthy town, Rudo and his foster father Legto try to coexist with the rest of the town's residents, but Rudo despises the wastefulness of the upper class. Ignoring the warnings from those around him, Rudo regularly rummages through the town's garbage in search of anything useful or valuable to save from the "Abyss"—a massive hole where anything considered trash is dumped, including people. Rudo's biological father was one such person, having been thrown into the Abyss after he was accused of murder.

One day, after running into a mysterious figure on the way home, Rudo returns to find Legto's dying body on the floor. He is immediately found at the scene by the authorities and is charged with murder. No one believes his claims of innocence, and he is thrown into the Abyss. Instead of dying, however, he finds himself in a strange, foul-smelling place surrounded by monsters made out of trash.

When Rudo is attacked by said monsters, he is saved by a man named Enjin, who reveals himself to be a "janitor"—someone who uses special weapons called "jinkis" to combat these creatures. In order to get his revenge on the one who killed Legto, Rudo reluctantly becomes a janitor to fight his way back up and out of the Abyss.

[Written by MAL Rewrite]

data.title: Tianting Ban Zhuan Xia
data.synopsis:
Li Ji, a cold and arrogant genius student in the Department of Architecture, was kidnapped by a creature from another world, Dark Qilin, and taken to a secret realm called Po Nian Space. The secret realm contained the ruins of an ancient heaven. Dark Qilin told him that he had to pass through if he wanted to go back. The test of heaven, and this test is to rebuild heaven...

(Source: iQIYI, translated)

data.title: Pororo Gonchung Daemoheom
data.synopsis:
One sunny day, Pororo played hide and seek with his new friend Bomi. Suddenly, they saw a strange light and turned small like bugs! After that, they met a honey bee 'Haney' who wants to become a singer. Haney is so bad at singing but she feels so happy while singing. Will Haney become a singer? Can Pororo and Bomi finish their adventure and successfully come back to home?

(Source: Amazon Prime)

data.title: Pororo Gonglyong Ppyeoga Sal-anassda!
data.synopsis:
One early morning, Pororo and his friends visit the nature history museum. Suddenly, the museum starts to shake, and the exhibits begin to tumble down! TongTong's magic spell misfires, and all of the exhibits come to life. Can our friends set everything back as they are? Come along for a wild museum adventure with Pororo and his friends!

(Source: Amazon Prime)
